title: Jen Kramer
itunes:title: Jen Kramer
description:
Taa Daa!  Whitney accidentally drinks a 112 proof margarita an hour before interviewing legendary magician Jen Kramer. We decided to air it anyway! Enjoy Whitney drunkenly trying to be a serious journalist. Go see Jen at her legendary residency at the Westgate Las Vegas or check out her website magicofjen.com/ because this will probably be the last time she agrees to come visit us.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
